---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import NavBar from "../components/NavBar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms &amp; Conditions"
  description="Terms and Conditions for Board Foot Calculator. Free to use, no warranties expressed or implied. Use at your own risk."
>
  <NavBar />

  <main class="bg-primary">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
      <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-caption-mono font-mono uppercase tracking-wide text-muted">
        Legal
      </span>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-display-xl text-primary">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-body-md text-muted">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-body-md text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-display-sm text-primary mt-8">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By using Board Foot Calculator, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the tool. We reserve the right to update these terms at any time.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display-sm text-primary mt-8">2. Use of the Service</h2>
        <p>
          This tool is provided free of charge for informational and estimation purposes. You may use it for personal, educational, or commercial projects. You may not reproduce, distribute, or scrape the tool for use on other platforms without permission.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display-sm text-primary mt-8">3. No Warranties</h2>
        <p>
          Board Foot Calculator is provided "as is" without any warranty, express or implied. While we strive for accuracy, the calculations are estimates and should be verified independently. We are not responsible for material shortages, overages, or any losses resulting from reliance on this tool.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display-sm text-primary mt-8">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          In no event shall Board Foot Calculator or its operators be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use this tool.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display-sm text-primary mt-8">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All code, design, and content on this site are the property of Board Foot Calculator unless otherwise noted. You may not copy, modify, or redistribute the tool's code or design without prior written consent.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display-sm text-primary mt-8">6. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of the United States. Any disputes shall be resolved in the appropriate courts.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display-sm text-primary mt-8">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms? Reach out through our <a href="/contact" class="text-accent-mustard underline decoration-accent-mustard/30 hover:decoration-accent-mustard">Contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
